This MIT license applies to the SOURCE CODE of Scan Vectorizer only
(scan_vectorizer.py, the PowerShell/batch build scripts, make_icon.py,
make_testpdf.py and the documentation).

Scan Vectorizer is a wrapper that drives several SEPARATE external programs
(Poppler, potrace/mkbitmap and Tesseract OCR). Those programs are NOT covered by
this license, are NOT included in this repository, and are downloaded by
`get_tools.ps1` onto your own machine. They each carry their own license
(Poppler and potrace/mkbitmap are GPL; Tesseract is Apache-2.0) — see
THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.
